Create a Doctor#show page that displays the doctor's name, department, and appointments, with each appointment's date, time, and patient name (linking to the patient's show page).

<h1><%= @doctor.name %></h1>
<h2><%= @doctor.department %></h2>
<h3>Appointments</h3>

<hr />
<ul>
<% @doctor.appointments.each do | appointment | %>
<li>
 <ul>
  <li>
    <%= appointment.appointment_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %H:%M") %>
  </li>
  <li>
    Patient: <%= link_to appointment.patient.name, patient_path(appointment.patient) %>
  </li>
  </ul>
</li>
<br />
<% end %>
</ul>
